      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNAP SHOT NZ (1) is a newcomer to the Brad Hewitt yard from NZ. Hasn't raced for nearly six weeks but the ace draw gives her every chance to kick off in Australia with a win. TIZZY LIZZIE (7) draws wide but worked from a similar draw when winning two back at this circuit and distance then raced parked again but stuck on for second last start at Albury, beaten 2.4 metres. Going well and if things go her way she has the talent to take care of this field. ASTRAL STRIDE (10) draws on the back row but is racing well and must be considered having produced two nice efforts since winning at Young. KIA ORA BEAUTY (5) was held up late when beaten 6m last week at Melton and was good when third at Bendigo prior.",
